        <prompt>What was the "Enforcement Act" of 1870 primarily designed to do?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Protect African American voting rights</option>
            <option letter="b">Regulate commerce</option>
            <option letter="c">Manage land distribution</option>
            <option letter="d">Control military forces</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The Enforcement Act of 1870 was designed to protect African American voting rights by providing federal enforcement of the 15th Amendment.</explanation>
